      <title>中国总理李克强对经济复苏充满信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/china-s-no-2-official-projects-confidence-in-economic-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国总理李强表示有信心政府能够实现经济复苏，同时也在贸易问题上对美国和欧盟进行了明显批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/china-s-no-2-official-projects-confidence-in-economic-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 03:03:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国警告称，俄罗斯升级干预美国选举的策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/russia-escalates-election-interference-tactics-us-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国情报机构在周一晚些时候（即选举日前几个小时）警告称，俄罗斯正在加大力度制造和传播虚假视频和虚假信息，以破坏美国大选的合法性并加剧本已很深的分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/russia-escalates-election-interference-tactics-us-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 02:03:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国加强反吸烟法，禁止在校外吸烟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/uk-toughens-anti-smoking-law-with-ban-to-apply-outside-schools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国将公布具有里程碑意义的立法，逐步淘汰烟草产品销售，打造第一批“无烟一代”，同时该法律草案还将强化在某些户外场所禁止吸烟的规定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/uk-toughens-anti-smoking-law-with-ban-to-apply-outside-schools</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为何摇摆州在美国大选中具有如此大影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/swing-state-history-why-2024-election-depends-on-7-battlegrounds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统大选的结果很可能被少数几个所谓“摇摆州”的数千名选民决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/swing-state-history-why-2024-election-depends-on-7-battlegrounds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
